<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>GreenRHINO</h1>
  <h2>A Dev-Match Community</h2>
  <h3>A membership site where entrepreneurs can meet developers.</h3>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="well">
      <h2 class="text-center">Silver Membership</h2>
      <br/>
      <h4 class="text-center">Sign up for a FREE Silver account to get basic access to the Developer Community.</h4>
      <br/>
      <p>The Silver Plan is free and will allow you to browse our lists of Developers and see 1 (one) example of thier work. It will not show contact information for you to contact the Developer.</p>
      <br/>
      
      <%= link_to "Sign up FREE!", new_user_registration_path(plan: @silver_plan.id), class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block btn-1' %>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="well">
      <h2 class="text-center">Gold Membership</h2>
      <br/>
      <h4 class="text-center">Sign up for a Gold account for $9.99/month to access the complete community, including contact info & resumes'.</h4>
      <br/>
      <p>The Gold account is a very low cost way to browse our list of Developers, including thier contact information, full portfolio and resume'. The $9.99 is a resonable fee for all the info you recieve.</p>
      <br/>
      
      <%= link_to "Sign up for Gold!", new_user_registration_path(plan: @gold_plan.id), class: 'btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block btn-1' %>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render "devise/registrations/banner_main" %>